Let E = Equity Implementation (0-1)
Let t = Time in years from implementation

The CORONA Protocol equation:

H(t) = 100 × (1 - e^{-k(Q×A×E)×t})

Where k = 0.3 (implementation efficiency constant)

With full implementation (Q=1, A=1, E=1):
  H(5) = 100 × (1 - e^{-0.3×5}) = 78% health security
  H(10) = 100 × (1 - e^{-0.3×10}) = 95% health security
